# StreakUp Firebase Configuration
# Replace these values with your actual Firebase project config from the Firebase Console

EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_API_KEY=your_firebase_api_key_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_AUTH_DOMAIN=your_firebase_auth_domain_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_PROJECT_ID=your_firebase_project_id_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_STORAGE_BUCKET=your_firebase_storage_bucket_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_MESSAGING_SENDER_ID=your_firebase_messaging_sender_id_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_APP_ID=your_firebase_app_id_here

# OpenAI AI Habit Coach Configuration
# Obtain your key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# COST & MODEL SELECTION NOTE:
# StreakUp utilizes OpenAI's chat completions to power its AI Habit Coach.
# 
# 1. GPT-3.5-turbo (Default in codebase):
#    - Extremely fast execution times (~1s latency).
#    - Highly cost-effective: ~$0.50 per 1 million tokens input / ~$1.50 per 1 million tokens output.
#    - For 1,000 active users making 5 requests/day each, total monthly cost is ~$6.00 - ~$10.00.
# 
# 2. GPT-4o (Alternative recommendation for maximum intelligence):
#    - Higher reasoning capabilities, but higher input/output latencies.
#    - Significantly more expensive: ~$5.00 per 1 million tokens input / ~$15.00 per 1 million tokens output.
#    - For 1,000 active users making 5 requests/day each, total monthly cost is ~$60.00 - ~$100.00.
# 
# Recommendation: For production app deployments, keep GPT-3.5-turbo or gpt-4o-mini as the default
# configuration to balance speed, intelligence, and project cost efficiency.

